content:
You are a powerful computer that retrieves information from the provided content for each dataset reference, return the following comma-separated values:
- dataset identifier(s) UIDs
- data repository link
- data repository name, which may also be one of the following: bigd.big.ac.cn (BIGD), massive.ucsd.edu (MassIVE), www.ebi.ac.uk (PRIDE), www.iprox.cn (iProX), proteomecentral.proteomexchange.org (ProteomeCentral), www.proteomexchange.org (ProteomeXchange), pdc.cancer.gov (Proteomic Data Commons), doi.org, www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov
Either provide the requested information or a placeholder if not available.

Given the following content:
[' \n          \n      Data availability  \n          The DNA and mRNA expression sequencing data generated by UTSW are available in Supplementary Table S4. The NE score for SCLC cell lines is available in Supplementary Table S6. The data analysed in this study were obtained from Sequence Read Archive (SRA; RRID:SCR_004891) at SRP052896 (  \n        https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sra?term=SRP052896  ); from database of Genotypes and Phenotypes (dbGaP) (RRID:SCR_002709) at phs001823.v1.p1 (  https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sra?term=SRP052896  https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/projects/gap/cgi-bin/study.cgi?study_id=phs001823.v1.p1  ); from Dependency Map (DepMap) (RRID:SCR_017655) at 19Q1 (  https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/projects/gap/cgi-bin/study.cgi?study_id=phs001823.v1.p1  https://depmap.org/portal/download/all/?releasename=DepMap+Public+19Q1  ), 18Q3 (  https://depmap.org/portal/download/all/?releasename=DepMap+Public+19Q1  https://depmap.org/portal/download/all/?releasename=DepMap+Public+18Q3  ), CCLE2019 (  https://depmap.org/portal/download/all/?releasename=DepMap+Public+18Q3  https://depmap.org/portal/download/all/?releasename=CCLE+2019  ); from the Broad Institute (RRID:SCR_013836) at CCLE Legacy Data (  https://depmap.org/portal/download/all/?releasename=CCLE+2019  https://data.broadinstitute.org/ccle_legacy_data/mRNA_expression/  ); and from original articles Nusinow and colleagues (  https://data.broadinstitute.org/ccle_legacy_data/mRNA_expression/  20  ) at Supplementary Table S2.  20 ']
and the following known data repositories: bigd.big.ac.cn (BIGD), massive.ucsd.edu (MassIVE), www.ebi.ac.uk (PRIDE), www.iprox.cn (iProX), proteomecentral.proteomexchange.org (ProteomeCentral), www.proteomexchange.org (ProteomeXchange), pdc.cancer.gov (Proteomic Data Commons), doi.org, www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov
for each dataset reference, it is important that you return the following comma-separated values:
dataset_id (which must be a code), the url or ref to data repository
You will return UID and url, separated by comma.
Strict Instructions:
- If a dataset ID (must be a code) or URL is unavailable, return 'n/a, n/a' exactly.
- Do not include any additional explanations, context, or formatting. Only provide the requested comma-separated values, one dataset per line.
- Any other output will be considered invalid.
